Subject: [PATCH 3/4] feat(exec): add main session policy for exec guard, SSH
 block, and output cap
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

PERSONAL BUILD v5: Stricter exec guard for main sessions:
- Main session + timeout > 30s → blocked (foreground OR background)
- Main session + timeout <= 30s → allowed
- Subagent sessions → no restrictions
- SSH/SCP/SFTP commands blocked in main session
- Output cap (default 50KB) for main session exec

Error messages direct users to sessions_spawn.
